            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crack the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>into a shallow bowl and beat lightly with a fork</p><p>Add 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to a plate with the <strong>southern fried seasoning </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>seasoned flour</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
